{
  "stem": "2830.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I came to the end when we had to leave.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was an announcement that the Russians are coming and everybody's got to leave.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That began the death march.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We walked on the death march.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my feet started to get worse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because, you know, I stopped this commander.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She gave me a little.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, and that started to heal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got worse.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the only thing she get-- she got me the pair of shoes instead of the wood.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I got a pair shoes she got me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that shoe-- those shoes saved my life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We marched about two days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I half-- a half a night, two days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the third, we stopped in a movie.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a movie house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, by marching, there's so many people, woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was only woman.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Died.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Either, you know, you try to make a wrong move the dog tear you apart, you know, the German shepherds.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or, when you behind, a little behind, or you got out of line, they kick you in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they didn't waste a bullet on you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They just kick you in, in the ditches.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you laid there until you die, or the ones that are already dead.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was just the most horrible thing you can only imagine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was already snow, high snow, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The cold was so very cold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my feet fave up on me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- they swell up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't felt I walked like on stilts, you know, like wooden feet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On stilts, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, on stilts.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we hit this-- we gonna rest for a couple hours.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the soldiers--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, they need rest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think they left for-- for a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
